parameters: \N<Village Chief> Oh, good morning Naoto-kun and Kaede-chan.
\N<Village Chief>What's the matter? This early in the morning.
\N<Naoto>Um, it's about the revitalization of the village....

\N<Naoto>This year, let us come up with ideas for revitalizing the
village!
\N<Village Chief>...Ah, did I really say something like that...?!

\N<Village Chief> That's right, that's right. I'm counting on both of
you then.
\N<Village Chief>Let's leave that to the two of you, shall we?

\N<Village Chief>Even if we talk about revitalizing the village, no
one would willingly come to a village like this....

\N<Village Chief>If you're having trouble deciding, how about
discussing it with Tanaka-san and the others?

\N<Village Chief>Of course it's okay. I want you to think about it
more casually.
\N<Village Chief>Are you going to work in the fields from now on?
\N<Village Chief>I see, I see. Do your best.
\N<Village Chief>Feel free to come by anytime, okay?
\N<Village Chief>Did you go into the Tanaka's house?
\N<Village Chief>Did you come up with a good idea?

\N<Village Chief>How is the revitalization of the village going,
hmm....
